  "body": "when indexed attestation stream tries to get committees of a non existing epoch in the future it gets into an infinite loop that causes the slasher to hang\r\n\r\n```epoch in the future, current epoch 14923, requesting 14924\r\n[2020-03-16 13:38:29] ERROR beaconclient: Could not receive attestations from beacon node error=rpc error: code = Internal desc = Could not retrieve committees for epoch 14924: rpc error: code = InvalidArgument desc = Cannot retrieve information about an epoch in the future, current epoch 14923, requesting 14924\r\n[2020-03-16 13:38:29] ERROR beaconclient: Could not receive attestations from beacon node error=rpc error: code = Internal desc = Could not retrieve committees for epoch 14924: rpc error: code = InvalidArgument desc = Cannot retrieve information about an epoch in the future, current epoch 14923, requesting 14924```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
